MALACAÑANG Manila

PROCLAMATION NO. 572

AMENDING PROCLAMATION NO. 460, S. OF 1932 WHICH RESERVED FOR SETTLEMENT FARM SCHOOL PURPOSES A CERTAIN PARCEL OF LAND OF THE PUBLIC DOMAIN SITUATED IN THE MUNICIPALITY OF TAGUM (NOW TAGUM CITY), DAVAO DEL NORTE, ISLAND OF MINDANAO, BY EXCLUDING FROM ITS OPERATION PORTIONS OF THE LAND EMBRACED THEREIN AND DECLARING THE SAME AS PERMANENT SITES OF THE DAVAO REGIONAL HOSPITAL AND BUREAU OF FOOD AND DRUGS-MINDANAO (BFAD) SATELLITE LABORATORY UNDER THE ADMINISTRATION OF DEPARTMENT OF HEALTH

Upon recommendation of the Secretary of Environment and Natural Resources, and by virtue of the powers vested in me by law, I, GLORIA MACAPAGAL-ARROYO , President of the Philippines, do hereby amend Proclamation No. 460, dated April 1, 1932, which reserved for resettlement farm school purposes of Barangay Apokon certain parcels of land of the public domain situated in Barangay Apokon, City of Tagum, Province of Davao del Norte, Island of Mindanao, by excluding from its operation portions of the land embraced therein and declaring the same as permanent sites of the Davao Regional Hospital and Bureau of Foods and Drug (BFAD) Mindanao Satellite Laboratory under the administration of the Department of Health, which parcels of land are more particularly described as follows:

Lot 595-A, Swo-11-000665 (Davao Regional Hospital)

A parcel of land (Lot 595-A, Swo-11-000665), being a portion of Lot 595, Cad-276, Tagum Cadastre, situated in the Barangay Apokon, City of Tagum, Province of Davao del Norte, Island of Mindanao. Bounded on the Northeast along line 4-5 by Lot 595-C of the subdivision plan; on the South west along line 8–9 by Lot 595-C and along line 9-1 by Lot 595-B, all of the subd. Plan; on the Northwest along lines 1-2-3 by Lot 595-B and along line 3-4 by Lot 595-G (Road Lot), all of the subd. Plan; Beginning at a point marked “1” on plan being S. 88°41’E.,. 1872.49 m. from BLLM 82, Cad-276, thence:

179.61 m. to point 2;

15.45 m. to point 3;

249.15 m. to point 4;

189.29 m. to point 5;

147.03 m. to point 6;

78.00 m. to point 7;

253.80 m. to point 8;

78.02 m. to point 9;

148.56 m. to point of

beginning, containing an area of SIXTY NINE THOUSAND NINE HUNDRED FIFTY FOUR (69,954) SQUARE METERS, more or less.

Points referred to are indicated on the plan and are marked on the ground as followed: all corners are G.S. cyl. conc. mons. 15 x 50 cm. Bearing true; date of original survey, April 1935 to July 1940 and that on the subdivision survey, May 28-31, 2003 executed by FNSP-J Chief of Party, Luisito A. Gacasan, and approved on October 10, 2003.

Lot 595-D, Swo-11-000665 BFAD-Mindanao Satellite Laboratory

A PARCEL of land (Lot 595-D, Swo-11-000665), being a portion of Lot 595, Cad-276, Tagum Cadastre, situated in Barangay Apokon, City of Tagum, Province of Davao del Norte, Island of Mindanao. Bounded on the Northeast along line 3-4 by Lot 595-C of the subdivision plan; on the Southeast along line 4-1 by Lot 2695, Cad-276, Tagum Cadastre; on the Southwest along line 1-2 by Lot 595-C, on the Northwest along line 2-3 by Lot 595-C, all of the subd. Plan; Beginning at a point marked “1” on plan being S. 65° 18′ E., 2173.00 m. from BLLM 82, Cad-276, thence:

151.39 m. to point 2;

297.89 m. to point 3;

151.42 m. to point 4;

197.86 m. to point of

beginning, containing an area of THIRTY THOUSAND (30,000) SQUARE METERS, more or less.

Point referred to are indicated on the plan and are marked on the ground as follows: all corners are “G.S.” cyl. conc. mons. 15 x 50 cm. Bearing true; dated on original survey, April 1935 to July 1940 and that of the subdivision survey, May 28-31, 2003 executed by FNSP-J Chief of Party. Luisito A. Gacasan, and approved on October 10, 2003.

IN WITNESS WHEREOF, I have hereunto set my hand and caused the seal of the Republic of the Philippines to be affixed.

DONE, in the City of Manila, this 9 th day of March, in the year of Our Lord, Two Thousand and Four.

(Sgd.) GLORIA MACAPAGAL-ARROYO

By the President: (Sgd.) ALBERTO G. ROMULO Executive Secretary

